{
  "id": "69b7eb4e5d41575f4a8d990a",
  "title": "～にすぎない",
  "created": 1773661008,
  "updated": 1773661745,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b7eb4e5d41575f4a8d990a",
      "text": "～にすぎない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661008,
      "updated": 1773661008
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7eb5f0000000000260b98",
      "text": "凄く高飛車で高慢な言い方に感じる（感想）[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661024,
      "updated": 1773661077
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7eb860000000000260b99",
      "text": "それでいて、「P だ」と言っても、「P にすぎない」と言っても、 P か not P かの真実性に変わりはない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661062,
      "updated": 1773661267
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ec620000000000260b9c",
      "text": "\t言い方で真実が変わるのであれば大変な事態だ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661282,
      "updated": 1773661316
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ec990000000000260b9d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661337,
      "updated": 1773661337
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ec9f0000000000260b9f",
      "text": "「～にすぎない」という言い方は所詮は修辞技法（レトリック）にすぎない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661344,
      "updated": 1773661745
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7edd800000000004b1f20",
      "text": "\tただ勢いに任せて押し切ろうとしているにすぎない。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661657,
      "updated": 1773661657
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ec9f0000000000260ba0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661344,
      "updated": 1773661344
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ec990000000000260b9e",
      "text": "[レトリック]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661337,
      "updated": 1773661342
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7eb5e0000000000260b97",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661023,
      "updated": 1773661023
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ecbb0000000000646774",
      "text": "もしかして:",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773661371,
      "updated": 1773661418
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ecc40000000000646776",
      "text": "[煮すぎない]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773661380,
      "updated": 1773661449
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ecc30000000000646775",
      "text": "\t[もしかしない]:[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661380,
      "updated": 1773661596
    },
    {
      "id": "69b7ece40000000000260ba2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1773661413,
      "updated": 1773661413
    }
  ]
}